<p>One key aspect of revolutionizing the DeFi ecosystem on ADA Layer 2 is through secure asset management enabled by smart contract layers. </p>



<p>Cardano&#8217;s layer 2 use cases provide a powerful solution for managing assets securely on the blockchain. By implementing smart contract layers, Cardano enables decentralized applications (dApps) to facilitate secure asset transfers, lending, borrowing, and other financial activities.</p>



