<p>To further enhance the potential of gaming and NFTs on Cardano, the platform can support large-scale NFT marketplaces and DApps, fostering the growth of novel applications in these areas.</p>



<p>With the implementation of layer 2 solutions, such as sidechains or state channels, Cardano can overcome scalability challenges and accommodate a high volume of transactions on its blockchain. This scalability is crucial for large-scale NFT marketplaces, as it ensures smooth and efficient trading of digital assets. </p>



<p>Additionally, it allows for the development of decentralized applications (DApps) that can handle complex operations and interactions.</p>



