<ul>
<li><strong>Ethereum Virtual Machine (EVM) compatibility:</strong> The ability of a Layer 2 platform to seamlessly interact with the EVM is crucial for interoperability with the broader cryptocurrency ecosystem, including decentralized exchanges and decentralized finance protocols.</li>



